                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Simple token bucket strategy. Return HTTP 509 (commonly used for &quot;Bandwidth Limit Exceeded&quot; but not in the HTTP spec) when request rate exhausts tokens. Note this is about request rate limiting, not about network traffic shaping. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
